sets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原版就煲N次都咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262708221899594424c1b13dab87f6caf134ce7e","tid":477152,"uid":139814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"唔好喊"},{"pid":"f11a403adda442458e2a86eaa735cbe15b9f63e9","tid":477152,"uid":56111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b80429206cc5945777e8f69271bd2507d3bd85","tid":477152,"uid":156659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"第五集爺爺嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"個人認為第5集最好睇<br />\n去到多田畀帽自己帶果度喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c6d92106c81c7fa626994c8f3ac728a2524794","tid":477152,"uid":56111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f11a403adda442458e2a86eaa735cbe15b9f63e9","tid":477152,"uid":56111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b80429206cc5945777e8f69271bd2507d3bd85","tid":477152,"uid":156659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"第五集爺爺嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"個人認為第5集最好睇<br />\n去到多田畀帽自己帶果度喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"第二句係指後面嘅集數，唔係第5集"},{"pid":"8ee29e4b0186642ef4d4c9386e3215998c723ca6","tid":477152,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"神劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fd22aa37673fceaa1242811f9a981929ca78f0","tid":477152,"uid":833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次睇唔太明，純粹當普通穿越劇睇<br />\n<br />\n第二次睇就再投入d,咖啡牛奶，棒球公仔果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常等到冇咩印象就會煲返，手機千尋緩存左全集<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n健三條仆街成日都讓機會白白流走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749c540916b6c9bf887885ad781ad9f8dd64eab2","tid":477152,"uid":14275,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得多田似mk多過健三<br />\n健三比較似死毒撚 不過佢地個殼就掉返轉<br />\n健三拖左咁撚多年都仲淆緊嘅時候 多田一諗要溝佢就即刻喺國王遊戲嗰陣扮傻鳩順勢表白  又比佢得米嗰下吹佢唔漲喎<br />\n又識氹女 唔似健三咁三日唔埋兩日就激嬲條女<br />\n不過多田都幾撚慘 婚禮都搞埋 條女先黎悔婚 <br />\n雖然睇到好撚爽<br />\n<br />\n好似離左題<br />\n不過睇個劇有咩好注意呀<br />\n淨係記住唔好開錯中國版囉"},{"pid":"837b5dc1478c85c602adeb662b79b86d0d815d68","tid":477152,"uid":117552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"一齊做哈利路亞chance<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700c10c5935c2f8f5c29f30ed66625a691b1670c","tid":477152,"uid":156659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"睇頭兩三集都無咩野<br />\n去到第四集開始憎健三，覺得佢成日浪費大好機會<br />\n去到第六集直頭覺得佢係抵死，想佢失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但去到第十集見佢心態改左，又好想佢成功，最後佢成功當然開心，但我又好唔開心見到多田老師咁嘅樣，到最後心情超矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c863ffdc6e70ce476d8897b59f5d2e0c9c06bd68","tid":477152,"uid":33410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T20:04:39.000Z","msg":"冇穿越 直接搶係冇可能搶到禮<br />\n靠既就係穿越 改變既每一小步<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外掛撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59a9e07d62a1d59d372461df81993ff5412a4fe","tid":477152,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"mytvsuper重播返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係冇點播"},{"pid":"d80